title: >>> The NUMBERS Game
body_text:
Below is an attendance chart from every single dodgeball event. DODGEBALL XXIV will easily be another unpredictable night, seeing how this past month as brought plenty of surprises. Who really knows what to expect come January 28th.
It is known however that Ryan McCrorey will be missing XXIV as well as Steve Adams, who hasn't missed an event since his debut at DAY 2. Could this be a prelude for things to come? That question will remain unanswered, at least until XXIV.
Whatever the case may be, you can bet that the night will be full of dodgeball action.
Take a guess ... what's the number for DODGEBALL XXIV ?
